ght: 30px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0;">Welcome back to Wall Power.=
 I=E2=80=99m <b>Marion Maneker</b>. I=E2=80=99m not an art advisor, but I p=
lay one in these pages. <br/><br/>In tonight=E2=80=99s issue, some thoughts=
 on the financial misadventures of Sotheby=E2=80=99s owner <b>Patrick Drahi=
</b>. His cavalier approach to debt makes for entertaining sport, especiall=
y as one watches his businesses dance above their snapping creditors. Sothe=
by=E2=80=99s, his personal trophy, is no different. Even with its recent in=
fusion of nearly $1 billion in cash from ADQ, the Emirati investment fund, =
there are still a number of questions surrounding whether Drahi will be abl=
e to hold on to control. More on this below.<br/></p>
