ouse? Sotheby=E2=80=99s says the deal, which has to be vetted by many juris=
dictions, needs regulatory approval before it closes later this year. (The =
E.U. gave the investment a thumbs-up last week.) <br/><br/>Sotheby=E2=80=99=
s already made deep cuts in London and Asia earlier this year. But when the=
