dGVybT1mNmM2MDYxN2RhNDJhYmQxMmEiLCJpbnRlcm5hbCI6ImY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSI=
sImxpbmtfaWQiOjEwNDY3Njl9/ccb2210672b989f5ba980bb3c40bcaff76776bc035332d30c=
5700c61bfd9b640" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bo=
ld" class=3D"sdf">subleased</a></u> the space starting in 2025. The wake-up=
 call is that the hospital won=E2=80=99t be paying rent for the first 15 mo=
nths=E2=80=A6 and then will pay 13 percent <i>less</i> than what Sotheby=E2=
